    ],
    "data": [
        [
            [
                ""
            ],
            [
                "As I open my eyes, I realize it’s just another day. "
            ],
            [
                "I swear I could hear my bed call out to me as I"
            ],
            [
                "stretch out of it with all the calmness in the world."
            ],
            [
                "I then look at the clock, and sigh in relief as It barely was 10 am"
            ],
            [
                "not too late but not quite early either."
            ],
            [
                "This day felt like a very chill one, with nothing to do really… "
            ],
            [
                "but that just can’t be right."
            ],
            [
                "I always have something to do."
            ],
            [
                "My phone buzzed as I wonder if there is something missing."
            ],
            [
                "A single message from Helpie hit me with realization."
            ],
            [
                "Hey… Where are you? the event is going to start soon"
            ],
            [
                "so better hurry if you want to find a good table!"
            ],
            [
                "THE QUICK-DATE EVENT! HOW COULD I FORGET?!?! "
            ],
            [
                "That’s right, after this event I was 100% guaranteed to find a partner."
            ],
            [
                "And to be honest, I wanted to find love more than anything in the world."
            ],
            [
                "Still… I forgot about it. "
            ],
            [
                "Maybe it was a sign... But as my phone kept buzzing with Helpie’s messages"
            ],
            [
                "I realized there was no time to think, it was time to RUN."
            ],
            [
                "Luckily, the cafeteria where the event would take place wasn’t too far away,"
            ],
            [
                "so It would probably take me 3 minutes to get there. "
            ],
            [
                "I approach the cafeteria, and my quick steps start becoming slower and slower, just to suddenly stop."
            ],
            [
                "There was this hopeless feeling that I tried to push away ever since I signed up to this."
            ],
            [
                "but overall, the question: ¿Am I really going to find true love here?"
            ],
            [
                "I thought you wouldn’t make it! Hurry! Let’s go and get you registered."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie began dragging me before I could protest. But maybe it was for the best."
            ],
            [
                "As I enter the cafeteria, I couldn’t help but feel overwhelmed by"
            ],
            [
                "all the corny hearts that conformed the decor of the place."
            ],
            [
                "but I really couldn’t blame the organizers for"
            ],
            [
                "choosing to go with a very on-the-nose theme for a dating event. "
            ],
            [
                "Helpie sat me on an empty table and handed me a presentation card. "
            ],
            [
                "Here"
            ],
            [
                "fill out this nametag so that others can know your name and your preferences!"
            ],
            [
                "Please let me know when you’re done."
            ],
            [
                "I fill it out and it says: ‘Hi! my name is: [tn], Hobbies:"
            ],
            [
                "Eating, sleeping, videogames, repeat."
            ],
            [
                "Awesome [tn], and just in time. The event is about to start, so let me give you a quick tip:"
            ],
            [
                "On your table, you’ll have a red and a green flag."
            ],
            [
                "The green flag is for all the people you match and feel attracted to!"
            ],
            [
                "so click it at the end of your date, and I'll save your decision list for later.."
            ],
            [
                "The red flag is for people who you don’t match with."
            ],
            [
                "Click it and they won’t be saved to your list."
            ],
            [
                "If you feel nervous, remember that I won’t be far away!"
            ],
            [
                "And [tn], I advice you to choose well…"
            ],
            [
                "Getting into a relationship isn't something to be taken lightly or to rush into."
            ],
            [
                "So take your time getting to know the people here, and even if you don’t find anybody, remember- "
            ],
            [
                "Suddenly, a high-pitched bell announces the beginning of the event."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie hurriedly gives me a thumbs up and"
            ],
            [
                "I signal them to walk back to give me some space."
            ],
            [
                "Soon after, people begin sitting on tables as I wait patiently for someone to approach me."
            ],
            [
                "But of course, everybody is just walking past little ‘ol me."
            ],
            [
                "‘Why did I even come here?’ I think as I get up from my seat."
            ],
            [
                "But out of nowhere, a smack on my table shakes me enough to make my legs"
            ],
            [
                "sit back down right where I was."
            ],
            [
                "I look up, and a big arm is on top of my table."
            ],
            [
                "Attached to it, a big teethed man with an ugly fedora just staring at me,"
            ],
            [
                "completely uninvited as I sit there dumbfounded. "
            ],
            [
                "He smells like a mix of sweat and cheap deodorant."
            ],
            [
                "Uhh… may I help yo-"
            ],
            [
                "Shh… I’m exactly what you need baby. My geekcord nametag is Johhney#6769"
            ],
            [
                "with tho h’s"
            ],
            [
                "what’s yours?"
            ],
            [
                "EXCUSE ME?????? WHO THE HELL IS THIS WEIRDO?? "
            ],
            [
                "And like HELL I’m gonna give him my nametag."
            ],
            [
                "I just look at him with the most disgusted face I’m sure I’ve ever had."
            ],
            [
                "I know baby. You must be surprised to have seen such a virile male among these omegas."
            ],
            [
                "But don’t worry… I’ll show you what you’ve been missing your whole life."
            ],
            [
                "This poor excuse of a human then begins puckering up and approaching me slowly."
            ],
            [
                "Is Johnney a green or red flag?"
            ]
        ],
